== 性質 ==
三複合立方體是一種由3個[[立方體|立方體]]互相嵌入所組成的複合多面體。這三個立方體沿著八面體群對稱性排列組成<ref name=h19>{{citation|contribution=Max Brücknerʼs Wunderkammer of Paper Polyhedra|last=Hart|first=George W.|title=Bridges 2019 Conference Proceedings|url=http://archive.bridgesmathart.org/2019/bridges2019-59.pdf|pages=59–66|accessdate=2021-09-04|archive-date=2022-01-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220121002229/https://archive.bridgesmathart.org/2019/bridges2019-59.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>，換句話說，立方體以斜45度的柱體方式沿著3個座標軸分布<ref name=h19/><ref name="Mattsson 2006">{{cite journal
|author = Mattsson, Ken and Ham, Frank and Iaccarino, Gianluca
|journal = Annual Research Briefs 2006
|url = https://www.researchgate.net/publication/240644012_Ecien_t_wave_propagation_on_complex_domains
|publisher = Center for Turbulence Research
|year = 2006
|pages = 223-233,
|title = Ecien t wave propagation on complex domains
|access-date = 2021-09-04
|archive-date = 2021-09-04
|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210904155013/https://www.researchgate.net/publication/240644012_Ecien_t_wave_propagation_on_complex_domains
|dead-url = no
}}</ref>，其對偶多面體為[[三複合正八面體|三複合正八面體]]<ref name="zefiro2010compound">{{Cite journal
  |title=The compound of three octahedra and a remarkable compound of three square dipyramids, the Escher's solid
  |author=Zefiro, Livio
  |journal=Visual Mathematics
